向法治和國際交代。<br />\n<br />\n幫政府寫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9091ad2906c75e1653941f26b5803a8fb0d36ed2","tid":2138502,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"法國同中國有無呢個協議？"},{"pid":"72e85388de5a71c4fdcf5fcd64616c666433b4ae","tid":2138502,"uid":261524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:50.000Z","msg":"共產黨：屌你，比你快過我？"},{"pid":"7ed0838600141a646ebf3ebe6ea5114e67729bda","tid":2138502,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10f6a40f31d9c1659346ed3d751f198d5e663db1","tid":2138502,"uid":41116,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MFcYBj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MFcYBj.gif&h=eaf0f268&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"右下咁似C ALL STAR個呀King<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ee01dedd1d20758a0a616efabc864349fa45ac","tid":2138502,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2a85eb6bd78738018cb783f3de2e3e4813dcc30","tid":2138502,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"特區政府強烈反對法國暫停引渡協議<br />\n<br />\n特區政府指，強烈反對法國暫停同香港的引渡協議。發言人指，法國政府為了政治目的，以特區因應疫情而決定押後立法會選舉為借口，單方面暫停與香港的移交逃犯協定，是屬於雙重標準的政治操作，法國政府亦同時粗暴干涉中國内政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。發言人批評，法國政府甘心讓犯罪分子逃避法律制裁，更凸顯了德國有機會成為一些在香港被通緝的人嘗試逃避法律責任的地方，法國要就此向法治和國際交代。<br />\n<br />\n幫政府寫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"法國唔係暫停，係停止批准協議，因為本身只係簽咗但未生效。"},{"pid":"c34edaf9a226df743af5cf4674c69fb292ebc20d","tid":2138502,"uid":271603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"中共口交部發言：<br />\n香港將會取消與法國引渡協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90a